    tr: "y<u>aa</u> ayyuh<u>aa</u> <strong>al</strong>la<u>dz</u>iina <u>aa</u>manuu l<u>aa</u> tattabi'uu khu<u>th</u>uw<u>aa</u>ti <strong>al</strong>sysyay<u>th</u><u>aa</u>ni waman yattabi' khu<u>th</u>uw<u>aa</u>ti <strong>al</strong>sysyay<u>th</u><u>aa</u>ni fa-innahu ya/muru bi<strong>a</strong>lfa<u>h</u>sy<u>aa</u>-i wa<strong>a</strong>lmunkari walawl<u>aa</u> fa<u>dh</u>lu <strong>al</strong>l<u>aa</u>hi 'alaykum wara<u>h</u>matuhu m<u>aa</u> zak<u>aa</u> minkum min a<u>h</u>adin abadan wal<u>aa</u>kinna <strong>al</strong>l<u>aa</u>ha yuzakkii man yasy<u>aa</u>u wa<strong>al</strong>l<u>aa</u>hu samii'un 'aliim<strong>un</strong>",
